596
00:44:15,170 --> 00:44:16,690
Nonsense.

597
00:44:17,090 --> 00:44:19,460
What's your relationship with Jiang Li?

598
00:44:19,690 --> 00:44:21,020
Shouldn't you be worried

599
00:44:21,860 --> 00:44:23,570
