600
00:44:24,570 --> 00:44:25,610
I see.

601
00:44:26,250 --> 00:44:28,820
You killed an official's daughter.

602
00:44:29,290 --> 00:44:30,460
I'm going to report you.

603
00:44:30,860 --> 00:44:31,730
Did you forget?

604
00:44:31,940 --> 00:44:33,540
